{"title":"Termux基础美化-zsh","date":"2020-02-22T13:11:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年2月22日","L":"2020/02/22","MM-DD":"02-22"},"thumbnail":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/cover.jpg","color":"#111","link":"posts/termux-zsh","comments":true,"tags":["Termux","zsh"],"categories":["瞎折腾"],"updated":"2020-02-22T13:11:00.000Z","content":"<p>看见别人的termux界面辣么漂亮，而自己的却是乌漆麻黑的，是不是很有差距？</p>\n<p>教你使用zsh代替bash作为默认shell</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>直接使用一键安装脚本安装</p>\n<p>方便快捷，一步到位</p>\n<p>复制以下内容粘贴到Termux即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gitee.com&#x2F;idkzr&#x2F;termux-ohmyzsh&#x2F;raw&#x2F;master&#x2F;install.sh)&quot; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>默认主题为 agnoster ，如需修改主题请编辑 .zshrc 文件</p>\n<p>将第一行 ZSH_THEME=“agnoster” 中双引号内的文字修改为你想使用的主题名称。</p>\n<p>输入zsht可调整字体及配色</p>\n<h2 id=\"zsht脚本截图：\"><code>zsht</code>脚本截图：<a title=\"#zsht脚本截图：\" href=\"#zsht脚本截图：\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/zsht.jpg\" alt=\"zsht.jpg\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"字体截图：\">字体截图：<a title=\"#字体截图：\" href=\"#字体截图：\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/fap.jpg\" alt=\"fap.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/fdsmfp.jpg\" alt=\"fdsmfp.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/fifp.jpg\" alt=\"fifp.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/fir.jpg\" alt=\"fir.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/fmfp.jpg\" alt=\"fmfp.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/frmfp.jpg\" alt=\"frmfp.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/fscpr.jpg\" alt=\"fscpr.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/fumdp.jpg\" alt=\"fumdp.jpg\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"配色截图：\">配色截图：<a title=\"#配色截图：\" href=\"#配色截图：\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/caci.jpg\" alt=\"caci.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/cflat.jpg\" alt=\"cflat.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/cgruvbox.jpg\" alt=\"cgruvbox.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/cmaterial.jpg\" alt=\"cmaterial.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/cpali.jpg\" alt=\"cpali.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/csolarized.jpg\" alt=\"csolarized.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/ctango.jpg\" alt=\"ctango.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/cura.jpg\" alt=\"cura.jpg\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/termux-zsh/cvag.jpg\" alt=\"cvag.jpg\"><br>\n主题推荐：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>本来是截了20个主题的图片的，但是手残，不小心del了，懒得截图了(◔◡◔)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Tips：<br>\n如果报错请带图反馈！</p>\n","prev":{"title":"可能是Windows上最强的开源任务管理器：Process Hacker","link":"posts/process-hacker"},"next":{"title":"基于Coding CI实现Hexo的持续集成与Github和Coding的同步部署","link":"posts/codingci"},"plink":"https://blog.zr.ci/posts/termux-zsh/","toc":[{"id":"zsht脚本截图：","title":"zsht脚本截图：","index":"1"},{"id":"字体截图：","title":"字体截图：","index":"2"},{"id":"配色截图：","title":"配色截图：","index":"3"}],"copyright":{"author":"箴扰","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.zr.ci/posts/termux-zsh/\" title=\"Termux基础美化-zsh\">https://blog.zr.ci/posts/termux-zsh/</a>","license":"本博客所有文章除特别声明外，均采用(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"nofollow\" targ